REPLACE:
    def get_file_symbols(self, file_path: str) -> list:
        """Get all symbols defined in a given file."""
        file_node = self.graph.find_node_by_path(file_path, node_type='file')
        if not file_node:
            return []
        return [self.graph.get_symbol_info(sid) for sid in self.graph.successors(file_node)]
